text: Godfreyhole is a hamletGodfreyhole, Derbyshire Dales - area information, map, walks and more Retrieved 2018-03-27. in Derbyshire, England. It is located at the junction of the B5035 and West End roads, west of Wirksworth, the population taken at the 2011 Census also included in the civil parish of the same name. ==References== Category:Hamlets in Derbyshire Category:Derbyshire Dales
